## INSTALL for I3WM

sudo apt-get install i3 conky acpi feh xautolock lxappearance clipit udevil blueman

# Adjust conkyrc.conf

Change BAT1 in the correct battery indicator.....

# Due to a bug in gnome-settings-daemon which makes the mouse disappear disable the following pluginA
dconf write /org/gnome/settings-daemon/plugins/cursor/active false

# fix nautilus to use with i3wm
add aliase nautilus = 'nautilus --no-desktop'

